{"tid":369990,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"腳甲倒生(嵌甲)邊度做手術好？","createTime":"2017-08-22T17:25:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T05:12:31.000Z","uid":112742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6cc78998862583c408c167e3ac010877ed63a25e","tid":369990,"uid":112742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T17:25:17.000Z","msg":"睇左兩次醫生食藥+搽藥膏都消唔到炎 佢叫我去做手術<br />\n好想做返運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n邊度有得快D做手術？<br />\n公立醫院要排幾耐先輪到？"},{"pid":"323685902af2abd969ac73b660877a6a0e213e44","tid":369990,"uid":116466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T17:27:12.000Z","msg":"雖然唔知 幫你唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但有冇圖睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6961d0cb187b5cfa79b5b4a53d88d2166e3e9d8","tid":369990,"uid":139093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T17:28:22.000Z","msg":"點解唔問醫生問連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb860775d18e26a9bb87fdb6ad28200ec1c22e6b","tid":369990,"uid":112742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T17:37:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解唔問醫生問連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇完醫生食藥以為好得返 食完哂藥冇睇過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd3cbb6d9b6847cfd1c18e17a541d3034bfc57da","tid":369990,"uid":129738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T17:49:17.000Z","msg":"診所都做到"},{"pid":"72c351aba176b226e38b80f8b0c0922551465c2d","tid":369990,"uid":70552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T17:50:52.000Z","msg":"以前係自己用美工刀切1/3指甲之後用鉗鉗出黎，痛撚到仆街不過好返"},{"pid":"a5dc8f