70bb485886","tid":369990,"uid":2986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T18:18:11.000Z","msg":"中三個時係仁安做兩隻腳趾公<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n過左一年一隻腳趾又發炎<br />\n一路發左幾年無理佢 之後自己好返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"811989272e4db35dd5a9d2df72339b1504e700a6","tid":369990,"uid":112742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T18:23:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中三個時係仁安做兩隻腳趾公<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n過左一年一隻腳趾又發炎<br />\n一路發左幾年無理佢 之後自己好返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n幾年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我想踢波啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69ede58cf69a2d195d0623cc788f6b4b6ce135a3","tid":369990,"uid":2986,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T18:29:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>中三個時係仁安做兩隻腳趾公<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n過左一年一隻腳趾又發炎<br />\n一路發左幾年無理佢 之後自己好返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n幾年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我想踢波啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個時一生腳甲就會插到個邊損哂 次次剪都痛撚到流眼水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 日日一除鞋都見到腳趾公位有血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋個時返學長期著襪著皮鞋 唔知關唔關事 傷口好唔到<br />\n反而返完學廢青個期唔使著鞋 就慢慢好返哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"596d3a9740c5c091b61ce13609c676aae1df2c5e","tid":369990,"uid":33635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T18:38:02.000Z","msg":"自己係屋企做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以前成日都會發晒炎咁<br />\n會揾指甲鋏中間個條嘢撩凸咗個條指甲出嚟<br />\n之後就剪咗佢<br />\n次次都整到標晒汗同眼水<br />\n但整完個下真係好爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5921825789a8255a14e3cdb8bd29fda267a5238","tid":369990,"uid":10581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T18:49:27.000Z","msg":"係仁濟做手術仔直接切咗兩邊等佢冇得再生，感覺良好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好過我係私家醫院度做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a876d29c21ec8fa993a2682daa474ee113327223","tid":369990,"uid":314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T19:05:15.000Z","msg":"試下淘寶搵 嵌甲矫正器"},{"pid":"2fb6a18ef86d533213207d4e8e6ede0a0ae38371","tid":369990,"uid":27939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T19:08:56.000Z","msg":"試過同一隻中2次<br />\n痛不欲生<br />\n有d診所有小型手術室已經做到<br />\n歷時5分鐘"},{"pid":"5a9258f25269bf5bc443521a4ca766d3fd7c5fb0","tid":369990,"uid":119804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-22T19:20:31.000Z","msg":"先後做左3次，公院手勢唔好好易復發<br />\n對上一次兩年前搵私家做，so far仲ok，理論上係可以斷尾<br />\n唔想再俾呢樣野纏擾嘅話我真係建議搵私家，最好係有經驗嘅外科or足科or骨科醫生"},{"pid":"1d53b0b22862d9fbba79126e3c52ade7e1b573a3","tid":369990,"uid":1587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T02:15:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我兩隻腳趾公都係<br />\n<br />\n我自己zip棉花整起塊甲等佢生出黎，唔再插肉<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一開流濃勁痛<br />\n<br />\n依加已經有三邊好返<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 以後唔好剪得咁入"},{"pid":"0df77747aa06b39d19394f524d9809590f7f0db7","tid":369990,"uid":112742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T16:05:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係仁濟做手術仔直接切咗兩邊等佢冇得再生，感覺良好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好過我係私家醫院度做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n要排幾耐？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f848b91085ca3a98f3a776f84938bed693b9c82a","tid":369990,"uid":23871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T16:46:19.000Z","msg":"公立啲門診如果有足疾就有得做<br />\n可以去睇左普通科門診 同醫生講 等佢轉介你<br />\n嵌甲係算足疾urgent case 一般兩星期內"},{"pid":"ce4f6e588316178a49ffacd96fc3e3f2d760bcce","tid":369990,"uid":33209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T17:08:40.000Z","msg":"細個成日倒生 唯一一次去睇醫生淨係洗傷口就搞掂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  已經唔記得洗左幾多日  淨係記得個護士姐姐好溫柔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}